title: Dakine Womens Pro II Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Women's Pro II pack in Turquoise.
Women's Pro II Features:
- Contoured harness designed specifically to fit a woman's frame
- Vertical snowboard carry
- Retractable cable ski carry
- Deployable helmet carry
- Fleece lined goggle pocket
- Top and back access entry
- Insulated hydro sleeve
- Snow tool/shovel pocket
- Quick draw ice axe sleeve
- Padded waist belt
- Rescue whistle
